      "writtenOn": "2021-04-16T22:35:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I mentioned the proto because today https://chromium.googlesource.com/infra/luci/luci-go/+/refs/heads/master/lucicfg/doc/README.md#resultdb.settings maps 1-to-1 to the proto. It will be somewhat confusing to have extra data in it that doesn\u0027t end up in the proto. Also at very least some documentation and/or lucicfg implementation will have to change.",
      "parentUuid": "ecd1ea4e_fd33e16a",
      "revId": "3706b0650fa5dd881a316c5443f690f868c50168",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
    },
